1. *Nastavio* sam da radim uprkos umoru. (I continued working despite being tired.)
2. On je *nastavio* da igra čak i kada je publika otišla. (He continued to dance even when the audience left.)
3. Kada je završio s poslom, *nastavio* je da razmišlja o svojoj budućnosti. (After finishing work, he continued to think about his future.)
4. *Nastavio* je put ka gradu nakon što je doručkovao. (He continued his journey to the city after having breakfast.)
5. Kada su se svi okupili, on je *nastavio* sa pričom o svom putovanju. (When everyone gathered, he continued with the story of his journey.)
6. *Nastavio* sam da učim srpski jezik kako bih bolje razumeo lokalno stanovništvo. (I continued to learn Serbian language to better understand the local population.)
7. Čim je stigao u Beograd, *nastavio* je da istražuje grad. (As soon as he arrived in Belgrade, he continued to explore the city.)
8. *Nastavio* je da se bavi sportom nakon što se oporavio od povrede. (He continued to engage in sports after recovering from the injury.)
9. *Nastavio* je da piše svoju knjigu uprkos teškoćama. (He continued to write his book despite the difficulties.)
10. Kada je video da ga niko ne sluša, on je *nastavio* da priča sam sa sobom. (When he saw that nobody was listening to him, he continued to talk to himself.)